prompts.frontCover: A whimsical, dreamy fantasy scene, flat 2D vector art style. An adorably grumpy cartoon gnome with a comically oversized, pointy red hat is sitting cross-legged on a giant, fluffy, magical mushroom. The gnome has a magnificent white beard and is stubbornly holding a tiny, brightly wrapped birthday present with a pouty expression. Surrounding the mushroom, a trio of mischievous, glowing fairies with translucent, iridescent wings are playfully floating around, teasing the gnome by tickling his beard with sparkling magic wands that leave trails of pixie dust. The background is a soft-focus, enchanted forest at twilight, with pastel colors of lavender, mint green, and dusty rose. Fantastical, gently glowing flora and swirling ethereal mists fill the air. Centered in the middle of the composition, elegant, readable, handwritten cursive script in a shimmering gold foil effect reads: "Don't be grumpy, it's your birthday!"
